This directory contains the sources that are branched off
the main repository periodically at the start of the release 
process.  The sources are tested, and bugs may be fixed.  When 
it is time to release the code, the sources are copied to a 
release directory, where the source remains frozen.  

Release numbers have two parts in the branch directory: "major.minor".

Release numbers have three parts in the release directory:
"major.minor.sub".

The source in this branch directory may continue to be modified,
after the initial release, with patch releases obtained by copying 
the improved code to the releases directory again and incrementing 
the third part ("sub") of the release number.
